      - ePost Digital LetterBox Identity Matching with detailed recipient feedback
      summary: Identity matching process.
      description: "Send metadata of your customers for matching them with ePost users.\
        \ The limit size of the metadata is 5 There is the possibility to hash the\
        \ metadata before sending it. It isn't mandatory to send all data for identity\
        \ matching, but the sent data has to be unique in it's combination.<br><br>The\
        \ access to this API request is restricted, because it returns detailed information\
        \ about whether a credential has been matched or not. Against a fee you are\
        \ able to use this detailed identity matching API. Please get in touch with\
        \ an administrator to get more information."
